0e9mon has a habit of collecting keys. It will sneak into people\u2019s homes to steal their keys."}, {"version": "sword", "text": "This Pok\u00e9mon is constantly collecting keys. Entrust a Klefki with important keys, and the Pok\u00e9mon will protect them no matter what."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "Long ago it lived in mines, but once the minerals that make up its diet became scarcer, Klefki began appearing in human settlements."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "Although it\u2019s unclear why it collects keys, giving it a key makes Klefki very happy. However, it apparently only likes master keys."}, {"version": "x", "text": "These key collectors threaten any attackers by fiercely jingling their keys at them."}, {"version": "y", "text": "It never lets go of a key that it likes, so people give it the keys to vaults and safes as a way to prevent crime."}], "entryGameVersions": ["alpha-sapphire", "moon", "omega-ruby", "shield", "sun", "sword", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun", "x", "y"], "moveGameGroups": ["omega-ruby-alpha-sapphire", "scarlet-violet", "sun-moon", "sword-shield", "ultra-sun-ultra-moon", "x-y"], "evolutionRows": [{"stage": 1, "name": "klefki"}]}